hadiths[92]{hadithnumber,text}:
4972,"Hammam-bin-Haaris ne Hazrat Adi-bin-Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! main sadhaaey huey kutton ko chhorta hun. wo mere liye shikar ko qaabu kar letey hain. aur main is par Allah ka naam bhi leta hun. ( bismillaah padhta hun (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum apna sadhaayaa hua kutta chhod do aur is par bismillaah padh lo to phir usko kha lo. maine kaha : chahe wo kuttey shikar ko mar daalein ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : chahe wo shikar ko mar daalein, jab tak koi aur kutta , jo unke sath nahi (bheja gaya), unke sath Sharik na ho jaey. maine kaha : main shikar ko moti lakdi ke naukdaar baghair paron ke teer ka nishan banata hun aur usey mar leta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum baghair paron wala teer maaro aur wo iske jism ko chhed de (khoon nikal jaey) to usko kha lo aur agar wo usey chaudai ki taraf se nishana banaey aur mar daale to mat khaao."
4973,"bayan ne Shabi se, unhon-ne Adi-bin-Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawal kiya ke ham log un kutton se shikar kartey hain? aap ne farmaya : jab tum apne sadhaaey huey kuttey chhod do aur is par bismillaah padh lo to jo (shikaar) wo tumharey liye pakdein chahey wo usey mar dein, tum usey kha lo, siwaey-iske ke kutta (is mein se) kuchh khud kha ley. agar wo kha ley to tum na khaao. kyonke mujhey khadsha hai ke usne apne liye (shikaar) pakda hoga. agar doosrey kuttey unke sath shamil ho gaey hain to mat khaao."
4974,"Muaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Abdullah-bin-abi safar se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Shabi se, unhon-ne Adi-bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se baghair par waley teer ke mutaalliq sawal kiya. aap ne farmaya : jab us ne apne ( chhedney waale) tez hissey ke zariey se nishana banaya ho to kha lo aur agar apni chaudai se nishana bana kar mar diya ho to wo chot lagney se maraa hua (shikaar) hai, usey na khaao aur maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kuttey ke (shikaar ke barey) mein sawal kiya. aap ne farmaya : jab tum (shikaar par) apna kutta chhod do aur is par bismillaah padho to usko kha lo. agar kuttey ne us (shikaar) mein se kuchh kha liya hai to usko mat khaao. kyonke kuttey ne us (shikaar) ko apne liye pakda hai. maine kaha agar main apne kuttey ke sath aik aur kuttey ko bhi dekhun aur mujhey pata na chaley ke donon mein se kis ne shikar kiya hai? aap ne farmaya : phir tum na khaao , kyonke tum ne sirf apne kuttey par bismillaah padhi hai, doosrey kuttey par bismillaah nahi padhi."
4975,"ibne-Ulaih ne kaha : mujhey Shoba ne Abdullah-bin-Ubai safar se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : maine Shabi ko kehtey huey suna, kaha : maine Hazrat Adi-bin-Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se baghair par waley teer ke mutaalliq sawal kiya, phir usi ki tarah bayan kiya."
4976,"ghandar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Abdullah-bin-Ubai safar se, unhon-ne aur kuchh doosrey logon ne jinka Shoba ne zikr kiya, Shabi se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Adi-bin-Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se baghair par waley teer ke mutaalliq sawal kiya, usi ki tarah."
4977,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : hamein Zakariya ne Aamir (Shabi) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Adi-bin-Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mea'raaz ke shikar ke barey mein poochha, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab laathi ki lohey wali taraf lagey to kha ley aur jab lakdi wali taraf lagey aur mar jaey, to wo ''waqeez'' hai (yani mauqooza hai jo patthar ya lakdi se maara jaey aur wo Quran paak mein haram hai) usko mat kha. aur maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kuttey ke barey mein puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab to Allah Taala ka naam lekar apna kutta chhodey , to kha ley lekin agar kutta shikar mein se kha ley to mat kha. kyonke us ne apne liye shikar kiya. maine kaha ke agar main apne kuttey ke sath doosrey kuttey ko paon aur ye malum na ho ke kis kuttey ne pakda hai? to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usko mat kha kyonke tu ney apne kuttey par bismillaah kahi thi aur doosrey kuttey par nahi padhi."
4978,Isa-bin-Yonus ne kaha : hamein Zakariya-bin-abi-Zayda ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki.
4979,"Saeed-bin-Masruq ne kaha : Shabi ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Adi-bin-Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo nehrain (ke qasbey ( mein hamarey hamsaaey aur hamarey paas aaney janey waley qaribi sathi they. unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye sawal kiya ke main shikar par apna kutta chhorta hun. phir apne kuttey ke sath aik aur kutta bhi dekhta hun ke usne usko shikar kar liya hai. aur mujhey ye nahi pata ke) asl mein) un donon mein se kis ne shikar kiya hai? aap ne farmaya : phir tum ( usko ( mat khaao , kyonke tum ne apne kuttey par bismillaah padhi hai, doosrey par nahi padhi."
4980,"Hakam ne Shabi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Adi-bin-Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne-Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
4981,"Ali-bin-mus'hir ne Aasim se, unhon-ne Shabi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Adi-bin-Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : jab tum apna kutta ( shikar par) chhod to bismillaah padho, aur agar wo tumharey liye shikar ko jakad ley aur tum us ( shikar ( ko zinda paogey to usko zabah kar do, aur agar tum shikar ko us haalat mein paogey ke kuttey ne usey mar daala ho aur is mein se kuchh khaya na ho. to usko bhi kha lo, aur agar tum apne kuttey ke sath aik aur kuttey ko paogey aur us ne shikar ko mar daala ho, to usko na khaao , kyonke tum nahi jantey ke usey un donon mein se kis kuttey ne maara hai. aur agar tum teer maaro to bismillaah padho, phir agar aik din tak wo ( shikar ( tumhen na miley ( baad mein miley (aur tumhen usmein apne teer ke ilawa kisi aur cheez ka nishan na miley to tum chaho to usko kha lo, aur agar wo tumhen pani mein doobaa hua miley to mat khaao."
4982,"Abdullah-bin-Mubarak ne kaha : hamein Aasim ne Shabi se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Adi-bin-Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se shikar ke mutaalliq sawal kiya. aap ne farmaya : aur jo to Allah ka naam lekar teer maarey phir to usmein apne teer ke siwa aur kisi mar ka nishan na paaey , to usey kha ley aur agar to usko pani mein doobaa hua paaey to mat kha . kyonke tumhen malum nahi ke wo pani se maraa hai ya tumharey teer se."
4983,"ibne-Mubarak ne Hewa-bin-shureh se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rabee-bin-Yazeed Dimashqi ko kehtey huey suna : mujhey abu-Idrees Aaizullah ne khabar di, kaha : maine Hazrat abu saulbaa khushni (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur puchha ke ya Rasulullah ! ham ahle-kitab (yani yahood ya nasara (ke mulk mein rahtey hain, unke bartanon mein khana khaatey hain aur hamara mulk shikar ka mulk hai. to main apni kamaan se, sikhaaey huey kuttey aur us kuttey se shikar karta hun jo sikhaya nahi gaya, to mujh se wo tariqa bayan kijiye jo ke halal ho. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ke tu ney jo kaha ke ahle-kitab ke mulk mein hain aur unke bartanon mein khaatey hain to agar tum ko aur bartan mil sakein , to unke bartanon mein mat khaao. aur agar aur bartan na milein to unko dho lo aur phir unmein khaao aur jo to ne zikr kiya hai ke tum shikar ki zamin mein rahtey ho to jis ko teer pahunchey aur to is par Allah ka naam lekar chhodey, to usey kha ley aur agar to apne shikaari kuttey se shikar karey aur is par Allah ka naam lekar chhoda ho to kha ley aur agar aisey kuttey ka shikar ho jo shikaari na ho aur to usey zinda paaley to zabah karke kha ley."
4984,"Zuhair-bin-Wahab aur muqri donon ne Hewa se isi sanad ke sath ibne-Mubarak ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki, albatta ibne- Wahab ne apni riwayat mein kamaan ke shikar ka zikr nahi kiya."
4985,"abu-Abdullah Hammad-bin-Khalid khayyaat ne Muawiya-bin-Saleh se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Juber se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu saulbaa (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki : jab tum ( shikar par) apna teer chalaao aur phir wo tum se ghayab ho jaey, phir tum ko mil jaey to kha lo jab tak badbudar na ho."
4986,"Ma'n-bin-Esa ne kaha : mujhey Muawiya ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Jubair-bin-Nufair se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne saulbaa (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us shakhs ke barey mein, jisey teen din ke baad apna shikar miley, riwayat ki. (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ( jab tak badbudar na ho usey kha saktey ho. ( sakht thandey ilaaqon mein der tak sahi salamat rahega.)"
4987,"Muhammad-bin-Hatim ne kaha : hamein Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne Muawiya-bin-Saleh se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Alaa se, unhon-ne Mak-hool se, unhon-ne abu saulbaa-bin-khushni (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se shikar ke barey main apni hadis bayan ki, phir ibne-Hatim (Rehmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha : hamein ibne-Mehdi ne Muawiya se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Juber aur abu-zaahiya se, unhon-ne Jubair-bin-Nufair se, unhon-ne abu-saulbaa (Raziallahu anhu) se Alaa ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki, aur uski badboo ka zikr nahi kiya aur kuttey (ke shikar (ke barey mein farmaya : teen din ke baad bhi usko kha saktey ho, lekin agar us se badboo aaey to usko chhod do."
4988,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba, Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim aur ibne-abi-Umar ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Idrees se, unhon-ne abu-saulbaa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kachliyon ( nauk daar daant ( waley har darindey ko khaney se mana farmaya hai, Ishaq aur ibne-abi-Umar ne apni riwayat mein ye izafa kiya. Zohri ne kaha : Sham (Syria) mein aaney tak ham ne ye hadis nahi suni thi."
4989,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne abu-Idrees Kholani se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat abu-saulbaa khushni (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne har kachli waley darindey ko khaney se mana farmaya hai. ibne-Shahab Zohri ne kaha : ham ne hijaaz mein apne ulma se ye hadis nahi suni thi. yahan tak ke abu-Idrees ne, jo Sham (Syria) ke fuqaha mein se hain, mujhey ye hadis bayan ki."
4990,"Amr-bin-Haris ne kaha ke ibne-Shahab ne unhein abu-Idrees Kholani se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-saulbaa khushni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne har kachli waley darindey ko khaney se mana farmaya."
4991,"Imam Malik (Rehmatullahi-alaih) bin-Anas , ibne-abi-Ze'ib , Amr-bin-Haris , Younus-bin-Yazeed wghaira ne aur Mamar , Yousuf-bin-maajishoon aur Saleh sab ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath Yunus aur Amr ki hadis ki manind (tarah) riwayat ki. sab ne khaney ka zikr kiya hai. siwaey Saleh aur Yusuf ke. un donon ki hadis ye hai : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne har kachli (nokdar dant) waley darinadey (ko khaney) se mana farmaya."
4992,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne Malik se, unhon-ne Ismail-bin-abi-hakeem se, unhon-ne Ubaida-bin-Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : har kachliyon (nukiley dant) wala darinda , usko khana haram hai."
4993,ibne-Wahab ne kaha : mujhey imam Malik-bin-Anas ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
4994,"Muaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Hakam se, unhon-ne Memoon-bin-Mehran se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne har kachliyon (nauk daar) daant   waley darindey aur nakhunon waley parindey (ko khaney) se mana farmaya."
4995,Sahal-bin-Hammad ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
4996,"abu-Awana ne kaha : hamein hakeem aur abu-Bishr ne Memoon-bin-Mehran se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne har kachliyon ( nauk daar daant ) waley darindey aur panjon se shikar karne waley parindey (ko khaney  se mana farmaya."
4997,"Hushaim aur abu-Awana ne abu-Bishr se, unhon-ne Memoon-bin-Mehran se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana farmaya, hukm se Shoba ki riwayat ki hui hadis ki tarah."
4998,"abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir se riwayat ki, kaha : ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein bheja abu-Ubaida-bin-jarrah (Raziallahu anhu) ki imaarat mein Quraish ke aik qafley ko milney (yani unke peechhey) aur hamarey safar kharch ke liye khajoor ka aik thela diya aur kuchh aapko na mila ke hamein detey. saiyedna abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) hamein eik-eik khajoor (har roz) diya kartey they. abu-Zubair ne kaha ke maine saiyedna Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke tum aik khajoor mein kya kartey they? unhon-ne kaha ke usko bachchey ki tarah choos liya kartey they. phir is par thoda pani pi letey they, wo hamein Sara din aur raat ko kafi ho jata aur ham apni lakdiyon se pattey jhaadtey, phir unko pani mein tar kartey aur khaatey they. saiyedna Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ham samandar ke kinarey pahunchey to wahan aik lambi aur moti si cheez namudaar hui. ham uske paas gaey to dekha ke wo aik janwar hai jis ko anbar kehtey hain. saiyedna abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ye murdar hai (yani haram hai). phir kehney lagey ke nahi ham Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke bhejey huey hain aur Allah ki raah mein nikley hain aur tum ( bhook ki wjah se) majbur ho chukey ho to isko khaao. saiyedna Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ham wahan aik mahina rahe aur ham teen sau aadmi they. uska gosht khaatey rahe, yahan tak ke ham motey ho gaey. saiyedna Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, main dekh raha hun ke ham uski aankh ke halqe mein se charbi ke ghadey ke ghadey bhartey they aur is mein se bail ke barabar gosht ke tukdey kat-tey they. aakhir saiyedna abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) ne ham mein se terah(13) aadmiyon ko liya, wo sab uski aankh ke halqey ke andar baith gaey aur uski pasliyon mein se aik pasli utha kar khadi ki, phir jo oont hamarey sath they, unmein se sabse badey oont par palaan bandhi to wo iske nichey se nikal gaya aur ham ne iske gosht mein se zaade-raah (raste ka tausha) ke liye washaaiq bana liye ( washaaiq ubaal kar khushk kiye huey gosht ko kehtey hain, jo safar ke liye rakhtey hain) . jab ham Madina mein aaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur ye qissa bayan kiya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo Allah Taala ka rizq tha jo usney tumharey liye nikala tha. ab tumharey paas us gosht ka kuchh hissa hai to hamein bhi khilaao. saiyedna Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ham ne iska gosht Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas bheja to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko khaya."
4999,"Amr ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teen sau sawaaron ke sath hamein muhim par rawaana farmaya, hamarey ameer Hazrat abu Ubaida-bin Jarrah (Raziallahu anhu) they, hamein Quraish ke qafley ki ghaat lagaani thi, ham ( taqriban ( aadha mahina saahil samandar par thahrey rahe, hamein shadeed bhook ka samna tha. yahan tak ke ham ne darakhton se jhaadey huey pattey khaaey aur us lashkar ka naam jhadey huey patton ka lashkar pad gaya. to samandar ne hamarey liye aik janwar nikal kar phainkaa jis ko anbar kehtey hain. ham nisf (aadhe) maah tak usko khaatey aur uski charbi ko tel ke taur par istemal kiya, yahan tak ke hamarey badan asl haalat mein lot aaey. Hazrat abu Ubeda (Raziallahu anhu) ne uski aik pasli (peeth ka kaantaa) lekar usey gaarh diya, phir lashkar mein sabse lamba aadmi aur sabse uncha oont dhoonda aur us aadmi ko is par Sawar kiya, to wo iske nichey se guzar gaya aur us ( anbar ( ki aankh ke halqey mein aik jamat baith gaee. kaha : ham ne uski aankh ke dheeley se itney-itney matkey charbi nikaali. (safar ke shuruat mein) hamarey sath aik boraa ( barabar ( khajoorein thin. (pahley ( abu Ubeda (Raziallahu anhu) hamein eik-eik muththi khajoor detey they, phir eik-eik khajoor dene lagey. jab (ye bhi milna) band ho gain to ham ne samajh liya ke wo khatm ho gaee hain."
5000,"Amr ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ko patton waley lashkar ke barey mein bayan kartey huey suna ke (jab zaade-raah (raste ka tausha) khatm ho gaya to shuruaat mein) aik din aik shakhs ne teen oont zabah kiye, phir teen zabah kiye, phir teen zabah kiye, iske baad Hazrat abu Ubeda (Raziallahu anhu) ne usko mana kar diya (ke sawari ke janwar khatm honey lagey they)."
5001,"Hisham-bin-Urwa ne Wahab-bin-kaisaan se, unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein (eik muhim mein) rawaana kiya. us waqt ham teen sau they, ham ne apna-apnaa zaade-raah (raste ka tausha) apne kandhon par uthaya hua tha. (aur aakhir mein sab ka zaade-raah mila kar aik borey ke barabar hua.)"
5002,"imam Malik-bin-Anas ne abu-Naeem Wahab-bin-kaisaan se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teen sau ka aik lashkar bheja aur Hazrat abu Ubaida-bin-jarraah (Raziallahu anhu) ko uska ameer banaya. unka zaade-raah (raste ka tausha) khatm honey ko aaya to Hazrat abu Ubeda (Raziallahu anhu) ne sab ke zaade-raah ko zaade-raah waley aik thailey mein jama kiya aur ham ko zinda rehney ki khuraak detey they, yahan tak ke aakhir mein rozana aik khajoor milti thi."
5003,"Waleed-bin-Kasir ne kaha : maine Wahab-bin-kaisaan ko kehtey huey suna : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko bayan kartey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne saahil samandar ki taraf aik lashkar rawaana farmaya, main bhi us lashkar mein tha. jis tarah Amr-bin-Dinar aur abu-Zubair ki hadis hai. albatta Wahab-bin-kaisaan ki riwayat mein hai ke lashkar ne atthaara din tak us ( badi machhli (ka gosht khaya."
5004,"Ubaidullah-bin-muqsim ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne juhaina ki taraf aik lashkar rawaana farmaya aur aik shakhs ko uska ameer banaya, aur (uske baad) un sab ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
5005,"imam Malik-bin-Anas ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin Ali ( ibne-Hanfiya (ke do beton Abdullah aur Hasan se, un donon ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ali-bin-abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar ke din aurton ke sath mutaa karne aur paaltu gadhon ka gosht khaney se mana farma diya."
5006,"Sufiyan , Ubaidullah , Yunus aur Mamar sab ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur Yunus ki hadis mein hai : aur paaltu gadhon ka gosht khaney se mana farma diya."
5007,Hazrat abu-saulbaa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne gharelu gadhon ka gosht haram kar diya.
5008,Ubaidullah ne kaha : mujhey Naafe aur Salim ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne gharelu gadhon ka gosht khaney se mana farma diya.
5009,"ibne-Juraij aur Imam Malik ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar ke din paaltu gadhey ka gosht khaney se mana farma diya, halanke logon ko (bhook ke sabab) uski (sakht) zarurat thi."
5010,"Ali-bin-Mus'hir ne Shebani se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Ufa (Raziallahu anhu) se paaltu gadhon ke gosht ke mutaalliq malum kiya, unhon-ne kaha : khaibar ke din ham bhook ka shikar they, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they. hamein un logon (yahudiyon) ke gadhey Shahar se bahar nikaltey huey mil gaey. ham ne unko zabah kar liya, hamari haandiyaan (unke paktey huey gosht se) ubal rahi thin ke achcha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke manaadi ne ye elaan kiya : haandiyaan ulat do aur gadhon ke gosht mein se koi cheez na khaao. maine puchha : aap ne unko kaisa haram kiya tha (qatai ya ghair qatai?) unhon-ne kaha : (is hawale) se hamari aapas mein baat cheet hoti thi to ham (aapas mein yahi kehtey ke aap ne unko qatai taur par haram kiya aur is wjah se (unhein hamesha ke liye) haram kiya tha ke unke panch hissey nahi kiye gaey they ( khums alag nahi kiya gaya tha)."
5011,"abdul-Wahid-bin-Ziyad ne kaha : hamein sulaimani Shebani ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Abdullah-bin-abi-Ufa (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : jang khaibar ki raaton mein ham bhook ka shikar ho gaey. jab khaibar ki jang ka din aaya to ham paaltu gadhon par toot padey jab hamari haandiyaan unke gosht se ubalney lagin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke manaadi ne ye elaan kar diya ke haandiyaan ulat do, paaltu gadhon ke gosht mein se kuchh bhi na khaao. us waqt kuchh logon ( sahaba ( ne kaha ke unse isliye mana farmaya hai ke unka khums nahi nikala gaya aur kuchh ne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse qatai taur par mana kiya hai."
5012,"Adi-bin-Sabit ne kaha : maine Hazrat Bara aur Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Ufa (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, donon kehtey they ke ham ne gadhey pakdey. unko pakaaney lagey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke manaadi ne elaan kar diya ke (un) haandiyon ko ulat do."
5013,"Abu-Ishaq ne kaha : Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke khaibar ke din ham ne gadhey pakad liye, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke manaadi ne elaan kar diya ke haandiyon ko ulat do."
5014,Sabit-bin-Ubaid ne kaha : maine Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke hamein paaltu gadhon ke gosht (khaney) se mana kar diya gaya.
5015,"Jarir ne Aasim se, unhon-ne Shabi se, unhon-ne Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein hukm diya ke ham paaltu gadhon ka gosht phenk dein, kachchaa ho ya pakka hua. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi hamein unko khaney ki ijazat nahi di."
5016,Hafs-bin-Ghiyas ne Aasim se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
5017,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : mujhey pata nahi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un (paaltu gadhon ka gosht khaney) se is bina par mana farmaya tha ke wo logon ke bojh uthaney waley hain aur aap nahi chahtey they ke unka bojh uthaney ka zaria' khatm ho jaey ya aap ne (waisey hi) jange-khaibar ke din paaltu gadhon ke gosht ko haram qarar diya. (yani aisi kisi khas munaasibat (wajah) ke baghair , jab dekha ke log usey khana chahtey hain to uski hurmat ka elaan kara diya.)"
5018,"Hatim-bin-Ismail ne Yazeed-bin-abi-Ubaid se, unhon-ne Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khaibar ke din nikley, phir Allah Taala ne unke liye khaibar fateh kar diya. jis din fateh hui uski Sham ko logon ne bahut aag jalaai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : ye kaisi aag (jal rahi) hai? tum kis cheez par (kiya pakaaney ke liye) aag jalaa rahe ho? logon ne kaha : gosht par. aap ne puchha : kon se gosht par? logon ne kaha : paaltu gadhon ke gosht par. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haandiyaan ulat do aur unko tod do. aik shakhs ne kaha : (aap ijazat dein to) ham haandiyaan undel dein aur unhein dho lein? aap ne farmaya : ya is tarah kar lo."
5019,"Hammad-bin-Mas-ada, safwaan-bin-Isa aur abu-Aasim nabeel sab ne Yazeed-bin-abi-Ubaid se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki."
5020,"Ayub ne Muhammad (bin-Sirin) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar fateh kar liya to ham ne basti se bahar nikalney waley gadhey pakad liye aur unka gosht pakaaney lagey, itney main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke manaadi ne ye elaan kar diya : suno ! Allah aur uska rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tum ko un (gadhon ka gosht pakaaney, khaney) se mana kartey hain. kyonke ye napak hai aur shaitan ka amal hai. phir haandiyon ko gosht samet ulat diya gaya jabke wo iske sath ubal rahi thin."
5021,"Hisham-bin-Hassan ne Muhammad-bin-Sirin se unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : jis din khaibar ki jang hui aik aaney wala Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : Allah ke rasool ! gadhey kha liye gaey, phir aik doosra shakhs aaya aur kaha : Allah ke rasool ! gadhey khatm kar diye gaey, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya aur unhon-ne elaan kiya ke Allah aur uska rasool tum ko paaltu gadhon ka gosht khaney se mana kartey hain. kyonke wo paleed hain ya (farmaya) napak hain. kaha : phir haandiyaan us sab kuchh samet jo unmein tha ulat di gaien."
5022,Muhammad-bin-Ali ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke jange-khaibar ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne paaltu gadhon ka gosht khaney se mana farmaya aur ghodon ka gosht khaney ki ijazat ata ki.
5023,"Muhammad-bin-Bakr ne kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne khabar di, kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they, khaibar ke zamaney mein ham ne jangli gadhon (gorkhar ,zebraa) aur ghodon ka gosht khaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham ko paaltu gadhey ke gosht se mana farma diya."
5024,ibne-Wahab aur abu-Aasim ne ibne-Juraij se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki.
5025,"Abdullah-bin-Numair , Hafs-bin-Ghiyas aur Wakee ne Hisham se, unhon-ne (apni ahliya) Fatima se, unhon-ne (apni daadi) Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein ham ne aik ghoda zabah kiya aur usey (paka kar) khaya."
5026,abu-Muawiya aur abu-Usama donon ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki.
5027,"Abdullah-bin-Dinar se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se saandey ke mutaalliq sawal kiya gaya to aap ne farmaya : na main isko khata hun na haram karta hun."
5028,"Leis ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se saandaa khaney ke mutaalliq sawal kiya to aap ne farmaya : na main isko khata hun, na haram karta hun."
5029,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par they ke aik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se saandaa khaney ke barey mein sawal kiya to aap ne farmaya : na main isko khata hun na haram karta hun."
5030,Yahya ne Ubaidullah se isi sanad se usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
5031,"Ayub, Maalik-bin-Mighwal , ibne-Juraij , Musa-bin-Aqba aur Usama sab ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se saandey ke barey mein Naafe se riwayat ki hui Leis ki hadis ke ham mana riwayat bayan ki, albatta Ayub ki hadis mein hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas saandaa ( pakka kar) laya gaya to aap ne na usey khaya na haram qarar diya. Usama ki hadis mein kaha : aik aadmi masjid mein khada hua jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par they."
5032,"Ubaidullah ke walid Muaz ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne tauba Anbari se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Shabi se suna, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aap ke kuchh sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) they. unmein Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. itney mein saandey ka gosht laya gaya is waqt Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki kisi bevi ne ye awaz di ke ye saandey ka gosht hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : khaao , bila shubah halal hai lekin ye mere khaney mein (shamil) nahi."
5033,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne tauba Anbari se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Shabi ne mujh se kaha : tum ne Hasan ( Basri) ki Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan ki hui (mursal) hadis dekhi (suni aur likhi hui dekhi , aur iske mursal honey par ghaur kiya? ( main to Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath dedh ya do saal tak (uthtaa) baithtaa raha lekin maine unhein us hadis ke ilawa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se koi aur hadis riwayat kartey huey nahi suna. unhon-ne (is tarah) kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) mein se bahut se log (maujood they) unmein Sad (Raziallahu anhu) bhi shamil they. Muaz ki hadis ki tarah ."
5034,"Imam Malik ne ibne-Shahab se unhon-ne abu Amama-bin-Sahal-bin-Haneef se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke main aur Hazrat Khalid-bin-Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar gaey, itney mein aik bhunaa hua saandaa laya gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski taraf hath badhaney ka irada kiya, Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar jo auratein thin. unmein se kisi ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jo cheez khaney lagey hain wo aapko bata do, (ye suntey hi) aap ne apna hath kheench liya. maine puchha : ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! kya ye haram hai? aap ne farmaya : nahi lekin ye (janwar) meri qaum ki sar zamin mein nahi hota, isliye main khud ko is se karaahat kartey huey paata hun. Hazrat Khalid (bin Waleed ( (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : phir maine usko (apni taraf ( kheenchaa aur kha liya jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dekh rahe they."
5035,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne abu Amama-bin-Sahal-bin-Haneef Ansari se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke Hazrat Khalid-bin-Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ne jinhein saifullah kaha jata hai, unhein khabar di ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan gaey. wo un (Hazrat Khalid (aur Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khala thin. unke yahaan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik bhunaa hua saandaa dekha jo unki behan hufaida binte-Haaris (Raziallahu anhu) Najad se laai thin. unhon-ne wo saandaa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney pesh kiya. aisa kam hota ke aap kisi khaney ki taraf hath badha tey yahan tak ke aapko uske barey mein bataya jata aur aap ke samney uska naam liya jata. (is roz (aap ne saandey ki taraf hath badhaanaa chaha to wahan maujood khawaateen mein se aik khatun ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bataao ke aap logon ne unhein kya pesh kiya hai? to unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! ye saandaa hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hath uper kar liya to Hazrat Khalid-bin-Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha : ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! kya saandaa haram hai? aap ne farmaya : nahi lekin ye meri qaum ke ilaaqey mein nahi hota, mein khud ko us se karaahat kartey huey paata hun. Hazrat Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : phir maine usko (apni taraf ( kheenchaa aur kha liya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dekh rahe they lekin aap ne mujhey mana nahi farmaya."
5036,"Saleh-bin-kaisaan ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne abu-Amama-bin-Sahal se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne unse bayan kiya ke unhein Khalid-bin-Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Hazrat Memuna binte-Haaris (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaey, wo unki khala thin, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney saandey ka gosht pesh kiya gaya, usey umme-Hufaid-binte-Haaris (Raziallahu anhu) Najad se laai thin, ye banu-Jafar ke aik shakhs ke nikah mein thin. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt tak koi cheez tanaawul na farmatey they. jab tak ke aapko malum na ho jaey ke wo kya hai? phir unhon-ne Yunus ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya aur hadis ke aakhir mein izafa kiya aur unhein (Yazeed) ibne-Asamm ne ( bhi) Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) se (yahi) hadis sunai, unhon-ne un (Memuna (Raziallahu anha)) ke yahan parwarish paai. (unki walida barza binte-Haaris Ummul-Momenin Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ki behan thin.)"
5037,"Mamar ne Zohri se, unhon-ne abu Amama-bin-Sahal-bin-Haneef se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein do bhuney huey saandey pesh kiye gaey jabke ham sab Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan maujood they un sab ki hadis ki tarah unhon-ne (Mamar) Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki hui Yazeed-bin-Asamm ki hadis ka zikr nahi kiya."
5038,"ibne-Munkadir se riwayat hai ke abu Amama-bin-Sahal ne unhein bataya ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein saandey ka gosht laya gaya, us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar tashrif farma they aur unke sath Hazrat Khalid-bin-Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) bhi maujood they phir Zohri ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki."
5039,Saeed-bin-Jubair ne kaha : maine Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke meri khala umme-Hufaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein ghi paneer aur saandey hadiya kiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghi aur paneer mein se khaya aur saandey ko karaahat mehsus kartey huey chhod diya. ye (saanda) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke dasterkhaan par khaya gaya. agar ye haram hota to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke dasterkhaan par na khaya jata.
5040,"Shebani ne Yazeed-bin-Asamm se riwayat ki, kaha : Madina Munawra mein aik dulhaa ne hamari dawat ki aur hamein  terah(13) adad (bhuney huey) saandey pesh kiye. koi (usko) khaney wala tha koi na khaney wala. doosrey din mein Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se mila aur maine unko ye baat batai. unke ird-gird maujood logon ne bahut si baatein kin yahan tak ke kisi ne ye bhi kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : main usey na khata hun na roktaa hun na usey haram karta hun. is par Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : tum logon ne jo kaha wo munasib nahi hai. Allah Taala ne jo Nabi bheja wo halal karne wala aur haram karne wala tha (hillat aur hurmat ke hukm ko waazeh karne wala tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jis tarah tum samajh rahe ho. ghair waazeh baat nahi kartey they.) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan tashrif farma they aur aap ke qareeb Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) aur Khalid-bin-Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) they. aik aur khatun bhi maujood thi to unke samney dasterkhaan laya gaya jis par gosht tha, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko khaney ka irada kiya to Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : ye saandey ka gosht hai aap ne hath rok liya aur farmaya : ye aisa gosht hai jo maine kabhi nahi khaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon se farmaya : khaao . so us gosht mein se fazal, Khalid-bin-Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) aur us khatun ne khaya. Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : main to sirf us khaney mein se khaungi jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khayenge."
5041,abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas saanda laya gaya. aap ne usey khaney se inkar kya aur farmaya : main nahi janta ke shayad ye (saanda bhi) un qaumon mein se ho jin mein maskh hua tha.
5042,"abu-Zubair ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se saandey ke mutaalliq sawal kya, unhon-ne kaha : usey mat khaao aur us se karaahiyat ka izhar kya aur bayan kya ke Hazrat Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey haram nahi kya. bila shubah Allah Taala iske zariey se (bhi) bahuton ko nafa pahunchata hai, ye aam charwaahon ki ghizaa hai. (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne mazeed kaha : ( agar ye mere paas hota to main usey kha leta."
5043,"Dawud ne abu-Nazara se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik shakhs ne kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! ham saandon se bhari hui sarzameen mein rehtey hain, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamein kya hukm detey hain? ya kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamein kya fatwa detey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey bataya gaya ke bani-Israel ki aik ummat (badi jamat) maskh kar (ke rengney waley janwaron mein tabdeel kar) di gaee thi. (iske baad) aap ne na ijazat di aur na mana farmaya, Hazrat abu-Saeed (Khudri (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : phir baad ka ahad aaya to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah iske zariey se aik se zyada logon ko nafa pahunchata hai. ye aam charwahon ki ghiza hai, agar ye mere paas hota to main usey khata. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko na-marghoob mehsus kya tha. (usey haram qarar nahi diya tha.)"
5044,"abu-Aqeel Dorqi ne kaha : hamein abu-Nazara ne Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke aik dehati Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : main saandon se bharey huey aik nashebi ilaaqey mein rehta hun aur mere ghar walon ki aam ghizaa yahi hai. aap ne usko koi jawab nahi diya, ham ne us se kaha : dobara arz karo, us ne dobara arz ki, magar aap ne teen baar (dohraney par bhi) koi jawab na diya, phir teesri baar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko awaz di aur farmaya : aey dehati ! Allah Taala ne Bani-Israeel ke kisi giroh par laanat ki, ya ghazab farmaya aur unko zamin par chalney waley janwaron ki shakl mein maskh kar diya. mujhey ilm nahi, shayad ye unhi janwaron mein se ho, (jinki shakl mein un logon ko maskh kya gaya tha) isliye na usko khata hun aur na us se rokta hun."
5045,"abu-Awana ne abu Yaafoor se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Ufa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jangon mein shamil huey (jinke doran mein) ham tiddiyaan khaatey rahe."
5046,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim aur ibne-abi-Umar sab ne ibne-Uena se, unhon-ne abu Yaafoor se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki Abu-Bakar ne apni riwayat mein saat (7) jangein kaha, Ishaq ne chh aur ibne-abi-Umar ne chh ya saat (7) kaha."
5047,Shoba ne abu Yaafoor se ye hadis isi sanad se riwayat ki aur unhon-ne saat (7) ghazawaat kaha.
5048,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Hisham bin Zaid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham ja rahe they ke (maqam) marruz-zohran mein aik khargosh dekha to uska peechhaa kya. pahley log is par daudey lekin thak gaey phir main douda to maine pakad liya aur saiyedna abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas laya. unhon-ne usko zabah kya aur uska puth aur donon raanein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas bhejin. main lekar aaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko ley liya."
5049,"Yahya-bin-Yahya aur Khalid-bin-Haaris donon ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, Yahya ki hadis mein : uska pichhla hissey ya uski donon raanon ke alfaz hain."
5050,"Muaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein Kahmas ne ibne-bareeda se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Abdullah-bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne sathiyon mein se aik shakhs ko kankar se (kisi cheez ko) nishana banatey huey dekha to kaha : kankar se nishana mat banao , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usey na-pasand farmatey they. ya kaha, kankar maarney se mana farmatey they, kyonke uske zariey se na koi shikar maara ja sakta hai, na dushman ko) peechhey ( dhakelaa ja sakta hai ye ( sirf ( daant todta hai ya aankh phodta hai. iske baad unhon-ne us shakhs ko phir kankar maartey dekha to us se kaha : main tumhen bataata hun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usey na-pasand farmatey they ya (kaha :) aap us se mana farmatey they, phir main tumhen dekhta hun ke tum kankar mar rahe ho ! main itna itna (arsa) tum se aik jumla tak na kahunga (baat tak na karunga.)"
5051,Usman bin umr ne kaha : hamein Kahmas ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah khabar di.
5052,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Qatada se unhon-ne Aqba bin sehban se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kankar maarney se mana farmaya, ibne-Jafar ne apni riwayat mein ye bayan kya ke aap ne farmaya : ye na dushman ko halaak karta hai, na shikar maarta hai, bas daant todta hai aur aankh phodtaa hai. aur ibne- Mehdi ne (apni riwayat mein) kaha : ye ( kankar, roda) dushman ko halaak nahi karta (unhon-ne) aankh phodney ka zikr nahi kya."
5053,"Ismail bin-Ulaih ne Ayub se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) ke kisi qaribi shakhs ne kankar se nishana lagaya. unhon-ne usko mana kya aur kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kankar ke sath nishana banaaney se mana farmaya hai. aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye na kisi janwar ko shikar karta hai, na dushman ko halaak karta hai, albatta ye daant todta hai. aur aankh phodta hai. (Saeed ne) kaha is shakhs ne dobara yahi kya to Hazrat Abdullah-bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : maine tum ko hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se mana farmaya hai aur tum phir kankar mar rahe ho! main tum se kabhi baat nahi karunga."
5054,Saqafi ne Ayub se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
5055,"Ismail bin-Ulaih ne Khalid Haza se, unhon-ne abu-Qilaba se, unhon-ne abu Ashas se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : 2 baatein hain jo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yad rakhi hain, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne har cheez ke sath sabse achchha tariqa ikhtiyar karne ka hukm diya hai. isliye jab tum (qisaas ya had mein kisi ko) qatl karo to achchhey tareeqey se qatl karo, aur jab zabah karo to achchhey tareeqey se zabah karo, tum mein se aik shakhs (jo zabah karna chahta hai) wo apni ( chhuri ki) dhaar ko tez kar ley aur zabah kiye janey waley janwar ko azeeyat (takleef) se bachaaey ."
5056,"Hushaim , abdul-wahaab Saqafi , Shoba , Sufiyan aur Mansoor , sab ne Khalid Haza se ibne-Ulaih ki sanad se aur uski hadis ke ham mana hadis riwayat ki."
5057,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hisham bin Zaid-bin Anas-bin-Malik se suna, unhon-ne kaha : main apne dada Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Hakam bin Ayub ke yahan aaya, wahan kuchh log they, unhon-ne aik murghi ko baandh kar hadaf banaya hua tha (aur) is par teerandazi ki mashq kar rahe they, kaha : Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is baat se mana farmaya hai ke janwaron ko baandh kar maara jaey."
5058,"Yahya-bin-Saeed , Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi, Khalid-bin Haris aur abu-Usama, sab ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath hadis riwayat ki."
5059,"Ubaidullah ke walid Muaz ( Anbari ( ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Adi (bin Sabit Ansari) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kisi Rooh wali cheez ko (nishana bazi ka ( hadaf mat banao."
5060,Muhammad-bin-Jafar aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
5061,"abu-Awana ne abu Bishr se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se riwayat ki, kaha : aik martaba Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ka chand logon ke qareeb se guzar hua jo aik murghi ko samney baandh kar is par teer andazi kar rahe they, jab unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha to usey chhod kar muntashir ho gaey, Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye kaam kis ka hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us shakhs par laanat ki hai jo aisa kaam kare."
5062,"Hushaim ne kaha : hamein abu Bishr ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se riwayat ki, kaha : (eik baar (Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Quraish ke chand jawanon ke qareeb se guzrey jo aik parindey ko baandh kar is par teerandazi ki mashq kar rahe they aur unhon-ne parindey waley se har chookney waley nishaaney ke badley kuchh dene ka tay kya hua tha. jab unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha to muntashir ho gaey. Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye kaam kis ka hai? jo shakhs is tarah karey Allah ki is par laanat ho, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisey shakhs par laanat ki hai jo kisi zi Rooh ko takhta-e-mashq banaey."
5063,"Yahya-bin-Saeed, Muhammad-bin-Bukair aur Hajjaj-bin-Muhammad ne kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne bataya, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne janwaron mein se kisi bhi cheez ko baandh kar qatl karne se mana farmaya hai."
